        <span class="product-category">
            HIGH PURITY MATERIALS
        </span>

        <h1>
            Tungsten Powder
        </h1>

        <p>
            High-Purity Tungsten Powder for Cemented Carbides,
            Powder Metallurgy, Aerospace, Electronics and Additive Manufacturing.
        </p>

    </div>

